WEBVTT

01:27.400 --> 01:31.940
[The Dark Romance]

01:32.140 --> 01:34.910
[Episode 10]

01:47.120 --> 01:47.870
The Xinghan

01:50.039 --> 01:52.430
is the name of a freighter for which

01:52.680 --> 01:54.210
I dedicated half my life to.

01:55.200 --> 01:56.840
It's not just a ship,

01:57.229 --> 02:00.280
but a brand deeply engraved in my life.

02:03.000 --> 02:04.120
And my captain

02:05.040 --> 02:06.900
was wise and firm,

02:07.000 --> 02:10.150
like the North Star,

02:10.870 --> 02:11.670
guiding us

02:12.120 --> 02:13.000
on the vast sea.

02:13.560 --> 02:14.910
So, on behalf of

02:14.910 --> 02:17.510
Oceanvision International Logistics Group,

02:18.030 --> 02:19.470
I have decided to

02:20.190 --> 02:22.320
name this scholarship after Xinghan.

02:24.360 --> 02:25.079
I believe

02:25.850 --> 02:27.810
every student present here

02:28.150 --> 02:31.520
can be like the daughter
of the Xinghan's captain,

02:31.660 --> 02:32.630
who is also

02:32.910 --> 02:35.970
one of the committee members
of the Xinghan Scholarship,

02:35.970 --> 02:37.090
[Xinghan Sets Sail,
Building Dreams Together]

02:36.260 --> 02:38.030
your Ms. Yan Ling,

02:37.110 --> 02:37.700
[Xinghan Scholarship Donation Ceremony]

02:38.630 --> 02:39.930
braving the waves

02:41.310 --> 02:44.240
to finally reach your ideal shore.

02:48.310 --> 02:49.840
Xinghan Scholarship?

02:50.800 --> 02:52.150
At the donation ceremony,

02:52.150 --> 02:54.030
Yan Ling is in the center.

02:54.470 --> 02:54.960
What?

02:56.030 --> 02:56.430
Look.

02:57.350 --> 02:58.780
[Xinghan Scholarship Donation Ceremony]

03:00.310 --> 03:02.360
Is their boss called Ding Zhibo?

03:02.750 --> 03:03.680
How did you know?

03:03.840 --> 03:04.700
Do you know him?

03:04.870 --> 03:05.960
How could I not?

03:07.150 --> 03:09.120
He's such a famous entrepreneur.

03:09.960 --> 03:12.100
I've known about him since college.

03:26.190 --> 03:26.790
Ms. Yan.

03:28.430 --> 03:29.430
Ms. Yan.

03:36.190 --> 03:36.850
Yan Ling.

03:37.120 --> 03:38.120
Yan Ling, I'll send you home.

03:38.120 --> 03:38.750
Yan Ling!

04:45.240 --> 04:47.600
The most important part of the third step,
the Lure Trap,

04:47.600 --> 04:49.870
is the takedown you've been waiting for!

04:50.000 --> 04:50.659
That will be

04:50.750 --> 04:51.390
tonight!

04:57.720 --> 04:59.070
With the virtual identity of

04:59.070 --> 05:00.560
the racing driver Murong Baichuan,

05:00.560 --> 05:02.830
Xuan added 128 girls on WeChat,

05:02.830 --> 05:03.950
chatted with 52 of them,

05:03.950 --> 05:05.480
with an exchange of more than 10 messages.

05:05.480 --> 05:07.180
Your mission tonight is

05:07.430 --> 05:09.680
to help Xuan
take down the girl he asked out,

05:09.680 --> 05:10.390
to draw first blood!

05:10.390 --> 05:11.160
Alright!

05:11.160 --> 05:13.120
Thank you, thank you.

05:13.390 --> 05:14.810
Introduce yourselves!

05:14.920 --> 05:15.360
I am

05:15.600 --> 05:17.210
Murong's buddy,

05:17.270 --> 05:18.030
Night God,

05:18.600 --> 05:20.040
and I'm also a racing driver.

05:20.040 --> 05:21.330
[Night God, Racing Driver]

05:21.510 --> 05:22.800
I am a director!

05:22.870 --> 05:24.730
I want to use Murong as a prototype

05:24.750 --> 05:25.870
to make a movie.

05:25.750 --> 05:27.210
[Ouyang, Director]

05:27.430 --> 05:28.000
I am

05:28.070 --> 05:29.430
the nutritionist

05:29.510 --> 05:31.270
of Murong's team!

05:30.740 --> 05:32.190
[Kevin, Nutritionist]

05:32.260 --> 05:32.940
I am

05:33.120 --> 05:34.510
Murong's stylist,

05:34.720 --> 05:35.390
Wenwen!

05:35.409 --> 05:37.770
[Wenwen, Stylist]

05:37.920 --> 05:38.480
I am,

05:39.120 --> 05:39.600
um,

05:39.720 --> 05:40.750
Murong's att...

05:40.610 --> 05:43.640
[Qiang, Attorney]

05:40.750 --> 05:41.600
attorney!

05:43.750 --> 05:45.010
What do you want to say?

05:46.240 --> 05:47.640
Murong Baichuan,

05:47.800 --> 05:48.900
Night God;

05:49.270 --> 05:51.270
aren't the names too fake?

05:53.190 --> 05:55.120
Do you know why telephone scammers

05:55.120 --> 05:56.380
always have an accent?

05:57.600 --> 05:59.950
Those who become alert
when they hear dialects

05:59.950 --> 06:01.560
are less likely to be fooled!

06:01.560 --> 06:03.720
It is to screen out the smarter ones!

06:03.720 --> 06:05.320
With such a dramatic script,

06:05.430 --> 06:06.430
the girls who believe it

06:06.430 --> 06:08.560
are much easier to take down!

06:09.830 --> 06:11.310
You are so wise!

06:11.750 --> 06:12.360
Right.

06:12.800 --> 06:14.170
Ms. Wenwen here

06:14.270 --> 06:15.420
is our wingman.

06:15.600 --> 06:16.700
With a girl around,

06:16.830 --> 06:18.270
it's more likely that they will

06:18.270 --> 06:19.470
let their guard down.

06:19.510 --> 06:20.380
Xuan said

06:20.720 --> 06:21.720
this girl

06:21.720 --> 06:23.120
isn't very experienced.

06:23.360 --> 06:24.030
She will

06:24.120 --> 06:25.550
probably bring a friend.

06:26.270 --> 06:27.070
They're here.

06:29.870 --> 06:30.680
Hello, hello!

06:30.750 --> 06:31.320
Xiaoyi,

06:31.430 --> 06:31.950
right?

06:32.430 --> 06:33.290
Here. Sit here.

06:33.430 --> 06:33.950
First,

06:34.310 --> 06:35.430
isolate the target.

06:35.430 --> 06:37.870
Cut her off from everything
that's giving her a sense of security

06:37.870 --> 06:39.330
so she can only rely on you.

06:39.600 --> 06:41.000
I find you really pretty.

06:41.120 --> 06:41.580
Second,

06:41.950 --> 06:43.080
confuse the target.

06:43.260 --> 06:44.380
Hit on her friend

06:44.830 --> 06:46.700
to make her feel unattractive

06:46.720 --> 06:47.450
and ignored.

06:48.000 --> 06:48.750
Welcome!

06:48.750 --> 06:49.750
-Cheers!
-Third,

06:50.000 --> 06:51.390
remember the notion of an alpha male

06:51.390 --> 06:52.590
that I told you about?

06:52.950 --> 06:53.670
Today,

06:53.750 --> 06:55.750
Xuan is the center of attention,

06:55.830 --> 06:56.890
the alpha among us.

06:56.950 --> 06:57.770
As his buddies,

06:57.770 --> 06:59.000
-we must sing his praises.
-Murong!

06:59.000 --> 07:00.040
Here's a toast to you!

07:00.040 --> 07:02.240
I wouldn't be where I am today
without you.

07:02.240 --> 07:02.950
Murong,

07:03.430 --> 07:05.070
thank you for the job opportunity!

07:05.070 --> 07:05.730
Murong,

07:05.830 --> 07:07.390
thank you for the promotion!

07:07.390 --> 07:09.070
I hope Mr. Murong can star

07:09.070 --> 07:10.070
as the leading man

07:10.270 --> 07:11.190
in my movie!

07:11.390 --> 07:13.040
Let's all help each other out, OK?

07:13.040 --> 07:13.390
OK!

07:13.390 --> 07:15.310
Elevate him and belittle her.

07:16.070 --> 07:17.680
Now, all the elevated one needs to do

07:17.680 --> 07:18.750
to the belittled one is

07:18.750 --> 07:20.880
to give her the slightest validation.

07:21.160 --> 07:22.360
Don't you think

07:22.510 --> 07:24.070
a girl like Xiaoyi

07:24.070 --> 07:25.240
is the real catch?

07:25.800 --> 07:26.240
Right!

07:26.300 --> 07:27.120
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

07:27.360 --> 07:29.000
One look and I know
she's beautiful and kind.

07:29.000 --> 07:30.390
Exceptionally elegant.

07:30.390 --> 07:30.950
Fourth,

07:31.630 --> 07:33.960
we finally reach the most important part:

07:34.159 --> 07:35.360
push the boundaries.

07:44.480 --> 07:45.480
Murong,

07:45.480 --> 07:47.159
you are being too much of a gentleman!

07:47.159 --> 07:48.810
The girl is going all out.

07:48.870 --> 07:50.240
What are you waiting for?

07:50.240 --> 07:51.100
Exactly.

07:51.130 --> 07:51.820
Hurry!

07:52.000 --> 07:52.680
Come on!

07:52.680 --> 07:53.600
Tear it!

07:53.600 --> 07:54.240
Come on!

07:54.240 --> 07:55.220
Tear it now!

08:07.330 --> 08:10.490
[Lihai Renxin Hospital]

08:14.000 --> 08:14.750
You're awake.

08:14.750 --> 08:15.880
What happened to me?

08:16.600 --> 08:17.560
Why am I here?

08:18.360 --> 08:19.750
You drove home in the rain

08:19.750 --> 08:20.800
and got a high fever.

08:20.800 --> 08:21.800
You scared Jiale.

08:25.830 --> 08:26.630
W-Where...

08:26.630 --> 08:27.510
Where is Jiale?

08:28.120 --> 08:29.580
He's at home. Don't worry.

08:29.800 --> 08:31.600
I ordered delivery food for him.

08:31.600 --> 08:32.659
He saw you were sick

08:33.289 --> 08:34.510
and remembered I'm a doctor,

08:34.510 --> 08:35.480
so he called me.

08:37.270 --> 08:38.150
I'm so sorry

08:38.880 --> 08:40.080
to trouble you again.

08:40.909 --> 08:41.840
It's no trouble.

08:43.150 --> 08:43.480
Here.

08:49.770 --> 08:50.620
Jiale said

08:51.750 --> 08:53.610
you had an argument with your mom,

08:53.900 --> 08:55.160
and it seemed serious.

08:56.240 --> 08:57.840
He's very worried about you.

09:01.510 --> 09:02.570
He said his grandma

09:03.360 --> 09:04.360
is also a teacher,

09:06.030 --> 09:07.560
and she sounds very strict.

09:08.440 --> 09:09.440
She is also alone.

09:12.550 --> 09:13.790
Usually, such people

09:14.650 --> 09:15.780
have high standards

09:16.070 --> 09:17.530
and are very controlling.

09:20.540 --> 09:22.100
It's not what you think.

09:26.810 --> 09:28.070
Actually, many people

09:28.390 --> 09:32.190
have difficulty managing
their relationships with their parents.

09:32.750 --> 09:34.000
For women,

09:34.480 --> 09:37.080
a mother's influence
is especially profound.

09:37.550 --> 09:38.590
Many girls

09:39.120 --> 09:41.450
want to escape their mothers' influence.

09:42.120 --> 09:43.450
But they somehow always

09:44.150 --> 09:46.280
end up living just like their mothers.

09:47.510 --> 09:48.310
Just like you,

09:49.480 --> 09:50.740
you became a single mom

09:51.360 --> 09:52.670
just like your mother.

09:57.240 --> 09:59.570
The process of cutting the umbilical cord

10:00.630 --> 10:01.720
is very difficult.

10:03.320 --> 10:05.080
Sometimes it's even bloody.

10:06.400 --> 10:07.930
You must never feel

10:08.630 --> 10:09.830
that you are terrible

10:10.360 --> 10:11.150
or selfish.

10:11.600 --> 10:13.390
The fact is you don't owe anyone anything.

10:13.390 --> 10:14.360
I owe my mom a lot.

10:24.480 --> 10:25.680
My dad's accident...

10:30.080 --> 10:31.480
was caused by me.

10:39.060 --> 10:40.910
Why isn't your dad back yet?

10:41.270 --> 10:42.840
The food is getting cold.

10:43.650 --> 10:45.320
How about I page him?

10:45.630 --> 10:47.120
How can he check it while riding?

10:47.120 --> 10:47.960
It's all because of you.

10:47.960 --> 10:49.150
Aren't the cakes from the bakery

10:49.150 --> 10:50.480
at the gate good enough?

10:50.480 --> 10:52.540
You had to make him go so far to buy one.

10:52.720 --> 10:53.630
My dad said

10:53.630 --> 10:55.610
only that bakery uses real cream.

10:56.790 --> 10:57.790
Again with the "my dad."

10:57.790 --> 10:59.280
He just spoils you rotten.

11:00.440 --> 11:01.240
Must be my dad!

11:01.370 --> 11:02.730
It must be your dad.

11:04.120 --> 11:05.320
Hello, where are you?

11:09.220 --> 11:10.750
Yes, speaking. Who is this?

11:31.000 --> 11:31.670
Dad...

11:34.120 --> 11:34.790
Dad...

11:38.830 --> 11:39.830
Don't ever forget

11:40.610 --> 11:42.770
that your father died because of you.

11:44.590 --> 11:45.280
Dad...

12:05.560 --> 12:06.450
Cry it out.

12:08.090 --> 12:09.150
Don't hold it back.

12:10.630 --> 12:11.890
I feel like you've been

12:11.910 --> 12:13.510
holding it in for a long time.

12:17.440 --> 12:18.500
It's going to be OK.

12:20.540 --> 12:22.430
Everything will be OK, Yan Ling.

12:23.970 --> 12:25.130
Now I know why

12:26.120 --> 12:28.020
you reacted that way to the cake

12:29.870 --> 12:31.510
when we had a meal last time.

12:34.320 --> 12:35.390
Since then,

12:37.770 --> 12:39.830
I stopped celebrating my birthdays.

12:51.390 --> 12:53.250
Don't punish yourself like this.

12:55.320 --> 12:57.450
Actually, your mom must know deep down

12:58.120 --> 12:59.580
that it wasn't your fault.

13:01.270 --> 13:02.330
It was an accident.

13:03.910 --> 13:05.220
You can't let guilt bind you

13:05.220 --> 13:06.620
for the rest of your life.

13:07.750 --> 13:09.120
But I could never

13:11.140 --> 13:13.370
make up for such a mistake.

13:19.910 --> 13:21.030
So in your mind,

13:22.720 --> 13:24.320
mistakes are unforgivable.

13:25.960 --> 13:28.160
Just like how you treated Jiale before.

13:45.200 --> 13:46.860
No matter how big the mistake,

13:47.960 --> 13:48.810
I believe

13:48.910 --> 13:50.170
you have atoned for it.

13:56.240 --> 13:57.730
You don't need to hear

13:58.560 --> 13:59.890
any criticism

14:00.000 --> 14:01.390
from anyone anymore.

14:39.520 --> 14:40.640
It is Jiale's dad.

14:41.360 --> 14:41.960
Answer it.

14:46.080 --> 14:46.510
Hello?

14:47.840 --> 14:48.500
Y-Yan Ling.

14:48.550 --> 14:49.280
Listen to me.

14:49.390 --> 14:51.200
Take Jiale right now

14:51.200 --> 14:53.200
to the lobby of his tutoring center.

14:53.200 --> 14:55.600
J-Just say I dropped him off
for his Math Olympiad class

14:55.600 --> 14:58.050
and y-you're picking him up.

14:58.200 --> 14:59.150
N-No, no.

14:59.150 --> 15:00.120
Don't ask why right now.

15:00.120 --> 15:01.890
I don't have time to explain.

15:01.960 --> 15:03.550
Don't forget to bring his backpack.

15:03.550 --> 15:05.320
Also, bring me a T-shirt

15:05.480 --> 15:07.010
a-a-and a pair of slippers.

15:08.840 --> 15:10.450
A-And also a hat!

15:10.600 --> 15:11.630
H-Hurry up.

15:11.670 --> 15:13.330
I'll wait for you downstairs.

15:14.460 --> 15:15.600
OK, I got it.

15:15.130 --> 15:17.650
[Nursing Rounds and Consultation System]

15:23.810 --> 15:27.130
[Emergency]

15:33.030 --> 15:34.960
You sure you don't need me to take you?

15:34.960 --> 15:35.440
No need.

15:37.550 --> 15:38.910
I don't have many clothes in my duty room.

15:38.910 --> 15:39.570
Just these.

15:40.830 --> 15:42.560
I've left the medicine inside.

15:42.790 --> 15:44.120
Don't forget to take it.

15:44.600 --> 15:45.000
OK.

15:45.750 --> 15:47.000
[Emergency]

15:50.590 --> 15:52.250
Let me know when you get there.

15:59.150 --> 16:01.260
[Emergency]

16:06.030 --> 16:07.690
No matter how big the mistake,

16:08.110 --> 16:09.910
I believe you have atoned for it.

16:10.960 --> 16:12.480
You don't need to hear

16:13.270 --> 16:14.070
any criticism

16:14.750 --> 16:15.950
from anyone anymore.

16:29.510 --> 16:30.900
Are you really OK?

16:32.030 --> 16:34.210
Your face looks quite red.

16:34.250 --> 16:34.870
Does it?

16:35.550 --> 16:37.360
It might be from the fever.

16:38.600 --> 16:39.910
My fever is gone now.

16:40.150 --> 16:40.750
I'm fine.

16:40.750 --> 16:42.120
When I saw you had a fever,

16:42.120 --> 16:43.910
I called Dad first.

16:44.670 --> 16:47.240
I only called Dr. Luo
because he didn't answer.

16:47.240 --> 16:47.820
I know.

16:48.150 --> 16:48.790
Thank you.

16:50.960 --> 16:53.030
What is Dad doing late at night?

16:53.240 --> 16:55.530
Why did you give him Dr. Luo's clothes?

16:58.080 --> 16:58.510
Lu.

17:00.820 --> 17:01.680
What happened?

17:02.200 --> 17:03.320
Don't say anything later.

17:03.320 --> 17:04.720
Neither of you say a word.

17:05.829 --> 17:06.650
Ms. Fang Fang.

17:09.400 --> 17:10.000
Fang Fang.

17:11.510 --> 17:12.440
You really came.

17:12.829 --> 17:14.089
You are unbelievable.

17:14.220 --> 17:15.589
You'd rather believe your besties

17:15.589 --> 17:16.920
than believe me, right?

17:17.109 --> 17:17.720
I mean,

17:17.950 --> 17:19.829
they were so sure about it.

17:20.109 --> 17:21.109
I don't see you!

17:21.109 --> 17:22.000
Where are you?

17:23.310 --> 17:24.240
Right, I'm here—

17:26.069 --> 17:26.480
Wait...

17:26.480 --> 17:27.280
Wait a second.

17:30.400 --> 17:31.830
I-I'll show you the photo.

17:31.830 --> 17:32.490
What photo?

17:32.880 --> 17:34.070
What do you want to show?

17:34.070 --> 17:35.870
Look, it looks exactly like you.

17:37.590 --> 17:38.240
Jiale, look,

17:38.240 --> 17:39.900
doesn't he look like your dad?

17:40.110 --> 17:40.990
It really does.

17:41.160 --> 17:43.330
-See...
-Fine, that's me, OK?

17:43.550 --> 17:44.750
Then how am I here now?

17:45.110 --> 17:46.770
Did I fly over here from there?

17:49.000 --> 17:49.830
Don't yell here—

17:49.830 --> 17:50.640
Don't!

17:51.350 --> 17:51.830
I know

17:52.720 --> 17:53.780
you look down on me.

17:54.030 --> 17:55.750
You are so much younger than me,

17:55.750 --> 17:56.750
and you've been trying everything

17:56.750 --> 17:57.950
to find fault with me.

17:58.200 --> 17:59.160
Enough, Fang Fang.

17:59.160 --> 17:59.680
It's not like that...

17:59.680 --> 18:00.960
I can understand that,

18:00.960 --> 18:01.420
really.

18:01.750 --> 18:04.210
-I was mistaken.
-But now you are starting to

18:04.790 --> 18:06.140
question my character!

18:06.270 --> 18:06.920
No!

18:07.750 --> 18:08.440
What do I have to do

18:08.440 --> 18:09.350
for you to forgive me?

18:09.350 --> 18:10.440
Fang Fang.

18:11.270 --> 18:12.720
How many times has it been

18:12.720 --> 18:13.270
already?

18:13.480 --> 18:14.030
Dad!

18:14.160 --> 18:16.020
When have I ever done this before?

18:17.200 --> 18:17.860
Seriously?

18:18.640 --> 18:20.880
You don't remember what you've done, huh?

18:20.880 --> 18:23.080
You don't remember how you hurt others!

18:23.510 --> 18:23.960
Right,

18:24.270 --> 18:25.550
that's just how you are.

18:25.550 --> 18:26.610
I'm not important.

18:26.830 --> 18:28.750
I'm not important to you at all.

18:30.440 --> 18:30.890
I...

18:31.440 --> 18:32.040
I'm tired.

18:33.070 --> 18:33.830
Now, I...

18:35.000 --> 18:35.590
I'm tired,

18:35.590 --> 18:36.030
OK?

18:36.880 --> 18:37.480
I'm tired.

18:41.350 --> 18:42.270
Ms. Fang Fang.

18:46.750 --> 18:47.750
F-Fine.

18:49.200 --> 18:49.720
Fine.

18:51.240 --> 18:52.040
Ms. Fang Fang!

18:56.920 --> 18:57.610
Dad!

18:58.510 --> 19:00.140
What's wrong with you?

19:01.160 --> 19:02.560
What's going on with you?

19:04.000 --> 19:05.030
Fang Fang has left.

19:05.030 --> 19:05.960
Go after her!

19:12.030 --> 19:12.960
She really left?

19:17.110 --> 19:18.570
What's wrong with you two?

19:23.550 --> 19:24.990
Don't be like me.

19:25.240 --> 19:26.370
It's not good at all.

19:30.110 --> 19:31.510
I signed up for that class

19:31.960 --> 19:32.720
for delivery riders.

19:32.720 --> 19:33.750
16,888, right?

19:34.240 --> 19:35.270
What?

19:37.270 --> 19:39.200
I'm talking to your mom about work.

19:39.830 --> 19:41.030
You really signed up?

19:41.200 --> 19:42.660
Didn't I learn it from you?

19:43.920 --> 19:44.590
If I didn't go,

19:44.590 --> 19:45.030
you...

19:46.070 --> 19:48.130
you might have done something crazy.

19:51.070 --> 19:52.270
So what did you learn?

19:53.440 --> 19:54.460
Didn't you see?

19:55.680 --> 19:57.480
Even someone like me can lie now.

20:02.050 --> 20:03.800
[Game Ruler]

20:03.550 --> 20:05.030
You've finished all the tasks

20:05.030 --> 20:06.230
before the third pit?

20:07.450 --> 20:09.290
You've managed to add 100 girls

20:10.070 --> 20:10.880
on WeChat?

20:13.790 --> 20:14.520
To be honest,

20:15.400 --> 20:16.440
I tried their tricks

20:16.440 --> 20:17.770
and they actually work.

20:18.160 --> 20:19.020
But it's mainly

20:19.310 --> 20:21.810
because I bought some small gifts in bulk

20:22.000 --> 20:23.270
to give away via QR codes

20:23.270 --> 20:24.570
that I filled the quota.

20:24.570 --> 20:25.240
[Five-Step Trap (Pit #3):
Lure Trap]

20:25.320 --> 20:27.220
[Five-Step Trap: Lure Trap]
[Definite] [Look Forward to]

20:25.640 --> 20:27.770
What about the final step of takedown?

20:29.590 --> 20:31.320
It's not time for that task yet.

20:38.550 --> 20:39.610
Take a look at this.

20:40.160 --> 20:41.890
The latest lesson of this term.

20:42.640 --> 20:44.440
Having passed the first 3 traps,

20:44.390 --> 20:48.670
[Five-Step Trap (Pit #4):
Destroy Her Self-Esteem]

20:44.440 --> 20:45.440
we've now reached

20:45.510 --> 20:48.350
the watershed of the Five-Step Trap.

20:48.920 --> 20:49.830
Put simply,

20:50.160 --> 20:52.780
the first 3 traps are
to make her fall in love with you.

20:52.780 --> 20:59.060
[Five-Step Trap (Pit #4):
Destroy Her Self-Esteem]

20:52.830 --> 20:54.200
The last 2 traps

20:54.550 --> 20:57.270
are to make her completely submissive

20:57.270 --> 20:59.000
so you can do whatever you want!

20:59.440 --> 20:59.880
Today,

21:00.680 --> 21:01.640
we are going to

21:01.640 --> 21:03.070
learn the fourth pit

21:03.090 --> 21:05.180
of destroying her self-esteem.

21:03.160 --> 21:07.720
[Five-Step Trap (Pit #4):
Destroy Her Self-Esteem]

21:06.070 --> 21:08.200
Only by destroying their self-esteem

21:08.310 --> 21:10.920
and turning them into
inferior beings in your world

21:10.920 --> 21:11.790
will they be unable to

21:11.790 --> 21:12.990
survive without you.

21:13.000 --> 21:13.530
This way,

21:14.000 --> 21:14.460
she will

21:14.510 --> 21:15.970
completely submit to you.

21:16.550 --> 21:17.200
In addition,

21:17.200 --> 21:19.000
as long as you don't plan to

21:18.010 --> 21:21.860
[Five-Step Trap (Pit #4):
Destroy Her Self-Esteem]

21:19.000 --> 21:20.240
grow old with your prey,

21:20.240 --> 21:21.590
you must execute the dump.

21:21.590 --> 21:22.400
And the dump

21:22.750 --> 21:25.070
is the most brilliant part of PUA Theory,

21:25.400 --> 21:29.330
and the touchstone for distinguishing
the masters from the mediocre.

21:31.350 --> 21:33.210
Destroy the prey's self-esteem,

21:33.590 --> 21:35.590
make her unable to live without you,

21:35.640 --> 21:36.960
and then dump her?

21:38.350 --> 21:41.480
Isn't this just
pushing people to their breaking point?

21:44.440 --> 21:46.440
Are you going to keep learning this?

21:46.680 --> 21:47.960
Of course I have to continue.

21:47.960 --> 21:49.240
I can't give up now.

21:49.720 --> 21:50.510
Didn't Zhang Yaozu

21:50.510 --> 21:51.770
learn up to this point?

21:51.790 --> 21:52.400
The point is

21:52.400 --> 21:54.250
there is no valid evidence here.

21:54.880 --> 21:57.010
It's almost the fourth and fifth pits.

21:57.200 --> 21:57.930
My mentor...

21:58.510 --> 21:58.880
No,

21:59.270 --> 22:01.070
I mean, those bastards have been

22:01.720 --> 22:03.160
acting so mysterious all day.

22:03.160 --> 22:03.710
I think

22:04.240 --> 22:05.070
at this stage,

22:05.070 --> 22:05.880
a lot of

22:05.880 --> 22:08.000
important evidence will be revealed.

22:08.000 --> 22:09.480
So I must keep at it.

22:09.550 --> 22:10.920
Otherwise, who knows how many people

22:10.920 --> 22:12.650
this toxic nonsense will harm.

22:19.240 --> 22:20.970
Liu Ping said he found Yu Kexin.

22:38.440 --> 22:40.170
I'm so sorry!

22:40.270 --> 22:41.640
After I parked my car,

22:41.720 --> 22:42.350
I got lost.

22:42.350 --> 22:44.310
I walked around for a long time
but couldn't find it.

22:44.310 --> 22:45.460
Girls usually

22:45.680 --> 22:46.400
don't have

22:46.880 --> 22:48.160
a good sense of direction.

22:48.160 --> 22:49.520
Don't laugh at me.

22:49.720 --> 22:50.180
I'm not.

22:59.160 --> 23:00.960
Why are you dressed so formally?

23:01.000 --> 23:01.750
You're so funny.

23:01.750 --> 23:03.020
You look like a groom.

23:04.550 --> 23:05.110
I...

23:05.790 --> 23:07.590
I'm not very good at dressing up.

23:08.270 --> 23:10.480
Dressing formally and festively

23:10.510 --> 23:11.570
can never go wrong.

23:12.310 --> 23:14.200
Thank you for taking this so seriously.

23:14.200 --> 23:16.120
From now on, I can help you

23:16.350 --> 23:17.350
with dressing up,

23:17.680 --> 23:18.880
if you don't mind.

23:21.000 --> 23:23.270
I don't mind. Of course I don't.

23:24.880 --> 23:25.540
It's great.

23:26.440 --> 23:27.480
I'd love that.

23:38.960 --> 23:40.880
I prefer men who are ambitious

23:40.880 --> 23:42.460
and responsible.

23:42.720 --> 23:44.950
I hope he can love and spoil me.

23:45.200 --> 23:46.920
I'll take good care of him too.

23:48.540 --> 23:50.560
For a man, career comes first.

23:51.030 --> 23:53.070
When he comes home
from working hard outside,

23:53.070 --> 23:55.270
I want to give him a warm haven.

23:58.240 --> 23:59.350
I think good girls

23:59.350 --> 24:01.210
shouldn't treat life like a game.

24:02.200 --> 24:04.780
So if there is someone suitable,

24:05.000 --> 24:06.590
I hope to get married early

24:07.110 --> 24:08.370
and live a steady life.

24:09.000 --> 24:09.680
Yes, yes.

24:10.790 --> 24:12.580
And I'm not young anymore.

24:12.790 --> 24:14.330
I really like children,

24:14.510 --> 24:17.490
so I want to have a baby soon.

24:17.680 --> 24:19.940
I will save my time for my children,

24:20.110 --> 24:20.770
my husband,

24:20.920 --> 24:21.720
and my family.

24:25.350 --> 24:26.480
H-Have some coffee.

24:32.070 --> 24:33.240
That's how it should be.

24:33.240 --> 24:34.200
Actually,

24:34.400 --> 24:35.480
I also want to find

24:35.960 --> 24:37.010
a simple girl

24:37.160 --> 24:38.430
and settle down soon.

24:38.830 --> 24:39.720
But nowadays,

24:39.720 --> 24:41.000
whenever marriage and kids are mentioned,

24:41.000 --> 24:42.930
many girls just shake their heads.

24:44.240 --> 24:45.170
Someone like you

24:45.720 --> 24:46.550
is quite rare.

24:50.790 --> 24:51.830
Can I help you?

24:53.240 --> 24:54.640
Let me introduce myself.

24:55.030 --> 24:56.160
I'm her ex-husband.

24:56.550 --> 24:56.920
Ex...

24:57.720 --> 24:58.750
Ex-husband?

25:00.030 --> 25:01.830
Which platform did you meet on?

25:02.350 --> 25:03.860
Did you spend a lot of money

25:03.960 --> 25:05.360
on a premium membership?

25:05.550 --> 25:07.280
Originally, for this meeting,

25:07.310 --> 25:08.550
you arranged to meet

25:08.590 --> 25:09.640
at the platform's

25:10.200 --> 25:11.270
offline center.

25:11.680 --> 25:12.680
When you arrived,

25:12.960 --> 25:14.290
she suddenly said it was

25:14.310 --> 25:15.200
too restrictive there

25:15.200 --> 25:17.350
and suggested
getting coffee nearby instead,

25:17.350 --> 25:18.550
and it'd be her treat.

25:18.830 --> 25:20.450
How do you know all that?

25:20.920 --> 25:21.790
Because that is

25:22.070 --> 25:24.400
exactly how she lured me in, step by step.

25:25.260 --> 25:27.310
Do you want to know
the rest of the script?

25:27.310 --> 25:28.400
Do you want to know

25:28.790 --> 25:30.590
how she tricked me into marriage

25:30.880 --> 25:31.640
and ruined me?

25:31.640 --> 25:32.350
Liu Ping,

25:33.510 --> 25:35.160
we are already divorced.

25:35.510 --> 25:38.030
I have the right
to pursue my own happiness.

25:38.400 --> 25:40.400
Slandering me like this won't help.

25:40.720 --> 25:41.680
It only makes me feel

25:41.680 --> 25:43.810
that leaving you was the right choice.

25:45.030 --> 25:46.000
He is a pervert.

25:47.070 --> 25:48.470
He physically abused me.

25:49.110 --> 25:51.110
There are police dispatch records.

25:51.310 --> 25:52.690
I escaped a marriage,

25:52.750 --> 25:54.440
hoping to find someone

25:54.720 --> 25:55.310
more reliable

25:55.310 --> 25:56.790
who can protect me.

25:57.920 --> 25:59.120
How could you do that?

25:59.790 --> 26:01.190
Hitting people is wrong!

26:02.110 --> 26:03.640
Mom!

26:07.480 --> 26:09.110
Mom!

26:09.480 --> 26:10.160
Xiaojie,

26:10.440 --> 26:11.370
why are you here?

26:11.790 --> 26:13.160
I missed you.

26:13.160 --> 26:14.510
Uncle Liu said

26:14.790 --> 26:16.920
he would bring Grandma and me to see you

26:16.960 --> 26:18.420
and give you a surprise.

26:18.680 --> 26:19.610
Is this child...

26:19.790 --> 26:20.880
He's not my child.

26:20.880 --> 26:22.480
I don't know who his father is either.

26:22.480 --> 26:24.000
You guys sort this out first.

26:24.000 --> 26:26.400
Let Grandma take you over there
to see the fountain.

26:26.400 --> 26:27.350
Buy him a piece of cake.

26:27.350 --> 26:27.790
OK.

26:29.200 --> 26:29.730
Let's go.

26:35.720 --> 26:37.050
How did you find me here?

26:37.960 --> 26:39.790
You changed the name on your insurance.

26:39.790 --> 26:41.320
Based on your son's ID card,

26:41.510 --> 26:42.570
I found your house.

27:01.720 --> 27:02.510
Is anyone in?

27:09.790 --> 27:10.590
Hello?

27:37.270 --> 27:37.920
Baby.

27:38.310 --> 27:38.970
We're home.

27:41.200 --> 27:41.880
Who are you?

27:47.680 --> 27:49.140
You really are crazy.

27:49.440 --> 27:51.290
You actually went to my home?

27:51.510 --> 27:52.200
Look at yourself.

27:52.200 --> 27:54.000
Is this how a man should act like?

27:54.310 --> 27:55.070
Sneaking around,

27:55.070 --> 27:57.000
you really disgust me, you know?

27:57.880 --> 27:59.210
Don't defend yourself.

27:59.750 --> 28:02.030
She just wants to use this PUA tactic

28:02.640 --> 28:03.970
to make you feel ashamed

28:04.270 --> 28:05.660
and lose your judgment.

28:05.880 --> 28:07.540
What PUA? I don't understand.

28:08.880 --> 28:10.090
Stop acting.

28:10.750 --> 28:11.920
Your tricks are

28:12.200 --> 28:13.880
to exploit others' sincerity

28:14.030 --> 28:15.760
to manipulate their feelings.

28:16.640 --> 28:17.430
Ms. Yan.

28:18.750 --> 28:19.990
You have a good brain

28:20.880 --> 28:22.400
and a family that supported your education

28:22.400 --> 28:24.060
to get you where you are today.

28:24.480 --> 28:25.350
But not all women

28:25.350 --> 28:27.240
are as lucky as you.

28:27.720 --> 28:29.270
Do women who aren't as smart or educated

28:29.270 --> 28:30.600
not deserve a good life?

28:31.930 --> 28:33.670
Your asset is your degree.

28:34.000 --> 28:36.200
Making rich men like me is my asset.

28:37.160 --> 28:38.640
We all work for a living.

28:39.550 --> 28:41.750
I don't think you're any nobler than me.

28:41.790 --> 28:43.810
At least I don't cheat and lie.

28:43.920 --> 28:44.480
Lie?

28:47.550 --> 28:48.110
Liu Ping,

28:49.880 --> 28:51.340
what did I lie to you about?

28:52.750 --> 28:53.830
Look in the mirror.

28:54.310 --> 28:56.160
Without your reputation, status,

28:56.160 --> 28:57.790
and your bit of money,

28:58.270 --> 28:59.920
do you think you deserve me?

29:02.350 --> 29:03.470
Between us,

29:03.720 --> 29:06.510
it has always been an equal exchange.

29:08.790 --> 29:10.270
If you're still resentful,
call the police.

29:10.270 --> 29:11.650
If it even works.

29:14.960 --> 29:17.360
You successfully avoided the legal risks.

29:17.880 --> 29:19.080
But we can expose you.

29:19.590 --> 29:21.390
Expose your way of making money,

29:21.640 --> 29:23.570
and let everyone know your tricks.

29:23.680 --> 29:25.080
Liu Ping can also sue you.

29:25.550 --> 29:27.480
Sue you for fraud when dividing property

29:27.480 --> 29:28.750
in the divorce.

29:29.920 --> 29:31.400
By then, your fake pregnancy

29:31.400 --> 29:34.200
and demanding compensation
can no longer be hidden.

29:34.200 --> 29:36.060
Let's see how you justify it then.

29:40.880 --> 29:41.510
Ask him.

29:42.640 --> 29:43.440
Will he agree?

29:44.880 --> 29:46.920
When a man like him feels humiliated,

29:46.920 --> 29:48.720
they'd rather kill themselves.

29:50.440 --> 29:51.880
I prefer men

29:51.880 --> 29:54.350
who are responsible and ambitious

29:54.640 --> 29:56.070
so he can spoil me.

29:56.070 --> 29:56.960
Don't leave me.

29:56.960 --> 29:58.000
Please.

29:58.020 --> 29:59.050
I beg you.

29:59.310 --> 30:00.550
Write a pledge.

30:01.480 --> 30:02.820
If I can't do it,

30:03.110 --> 30:04.350
I will leave with nothing,

30:04.350 --> 30:05.440
die a horrible death,

30:05.440 --> 30:07.040
and get struck by lightning!

30:08.110 --> 30:09.640
So you hit her?

30:10.510 --> 30:12.130
So I...

30:12.270 --> 30:14.390
I'm a bastard!

30:14.720 --> 30:15.550
This kind of drug is

30:15.550 --> 30:17.920
a state-controlled
Class II psychotropic drug,

30:17.920 --> 30:18.790
commonly known as

30:18.790 --> 30:20.590
obedience powder or date rape pills.

30:20.590 --> 30:22.590
Get an identical tattoo on your body

30:22.920 --> 30:23.980
to prove you love me

30:24.240 --> 30:25.970
and prove you belong only to me.

30:26.920 --> 30:28.920
What about the injuries on her body?

30:29.640 --> 30:31.920
She couldn't have beaten herself,
could she?

30:31.920 --> 30:34.200
All I know is I definitely didn't hit her.

30:34.310 --> 30:35.070
Xinxin.

30:35.720 --> 30:37.570
Who exactly are you?

30:38.200 --> 30:40.660
Why did you come to me?

30:41.960 --> 30:44.240
Is it because I'm stupid?

30:46.830 --> 30:47.550
I agree.

30:48.720 --> 30:51.520
Because I've already died once
when I was with you.

30:59.030 --> 31:00.430
What exactly do you want?

31:06.510 --> 31:07.640
I want to find Xia Yi.

31:11.300 --> 31:12.770
I was right, wasn't I?

31:12.960 --> 31:14.220
We both landed safely.

31:14.240 --> 31:16.400
You are getting more and more formidable.

31:16.400 --> 31:18.130
You can almost be my master.

31:18.240 --> 31:19.720
She's just too gullible.

31:19.880 --> 31:21.070
To think she's a university professor.

31:21.070 --> 31:22.400
Her intelligence is questionable.

31:22.400 --> 31:25.070
Isn't that because
the material I gave you was good?

31:25.070 --> 31:26.480
Her dad is dead, her mom doesn't love her,

31:26.480 --> 31:27.920
and she's single and pregnant.

31:27.920 --> 31:29.880
This is called synesthesia.

31:31.550 --> 31:34.080
Our teamwork makes us the perfect duo.

31:34.510 --> 31:35.400
Aren't I amazing?

31:35.400 --> 31:36.000
Nice!

31:36.530 --> 31:37.480
Not using a voice changer anymore?

31:37.480 --> 31:38.350
Only one left.

31:38.400 --> 31:39.490
Hit him. Hit him.

31:39.720 --> 31:40.160
Keep up!

31:40.160 --> 31:42.030
This is what they call an invincible

31:42.030 --> 31:43.360
-perfect match.
-Nice!

31:44.440 --> 31:44.970
Careful.

31:56.920 --> 31:57.750
Yu Kexin.

31:57.920 --> 31:59.850
I know you were scammed by them too.

32:00.590 --> 32:02.850
But don't keep going down the wrong path.

32:04.920 --> 32:06.480
Why are you so nosy?

32:06.480 --> 32:08.790
Won't you just stop pestering me
and leave me alone?

32:08.790 --> 32:10.680
When this nosiness is useful to you,

32:10.680 --> 32:11.550
you accept it.

32:11.920 --> 32:13.120
When it's not useful,

32:13.160 --> 32:14.680
you think it's pestering.

32:16.480 --> 32:19.000
When you didn't want me
to investigate further,

32:19.000 --> 32:20.960
you deliberately came to me
to show me your tattoo

32:20.960 --> 32:23.750
to make me believe Leilei
also took out a loan with her nudes.

32:23.750 --> 32:24.880
You are too greedy.

32:25.920 --> 32:27.720
If you had rejected me when I offered

32:27.720 --> 32:29.050
to find you an attorney,

32:29.240 --> 32:30.440
I might still

32:30.790 --> 32:32.990
not have found the flaw in your schemes.

32:35.790 --> 32:36.690
You know what?

32:37.240 --> 32:39.070
Liu Ping was hurt so badly by you,

32:39.510 --> 32:41.400
but he is still worried about you.

32:43.310 --> 32:44.640
He's afraid that if you scam someone

32:44.640 --> 32:45.770
who isn't so kind,

32:45.960 --> 32:48.360
you might get retaliated against and hurt.

32:51.270 --> 32:52.330
For someone like me

32:53.350 --> 32:54.150
who has a child

32:55.030 --> 32:55.790
and a past,

32:56.830 --> 32:59.480
if I didn't get all dolled up
and pretend to be naive and rich,

32:59.480 --> 33:01.210
which man would even look at me?

33:01.960 --> 33:04.690
Shouldn't the fact that
you have a child and a past

33:05.680 --> 33:06.780
make you want to

33:06.880 --> 33:08.030
make a clean break with

33:08.030 --> 33:09.430
all that pain and deceit?

33:11.200 --> 33:12.960
Would you want your son to live

33:13.680 --> 33:15.680
in a world of deception like you?

33:16.780 --> 33:17.870
I am a mom too.

33:19.070 --> 33:20.270
I wouldn't want that.

33:26.880 --> 33:27.430
Xuan,

33:27.830 --> 33:29.520
you've improved very fast.

33:29.790 --> 33:31.400
Everyone should learn from Xuan

33:31.400 --> 33:32.550
and keep up the good work,

33:32.550 --> 33:33.200
alright?

33:33.200 --> 33:34.440
Yes!

33:34.480 --> 33:35.870
[Love Guide]

33:39.200 --> 33:40.440
What... What is this good stuff?

33:40.440 --> 33:41.070
Let me learn too.

33:41.070 --> 33:42.070
Qiang, come here.

33:43.470 --> 33:44.070
Come here.

33:44.680 --> 33:46.180
[Love Guide]

33:45.480 --> 33:46.280
Let me ask you,

33:46.340 --> 33:48.140
what is the core of team battles?

33:49.650 --> 33:50.520
It is...

33:50.550 --> 33:50.920
It's...

33:50.920 --> 33:52.250
The core of team battles

33:52.310 --> 33:53.550
is supporting

33:53.550 --> 33:54.880
and helping each other.

33:55.000 --> 33:57.070
Slipping away midway was too wicked.

33:57.270 --> 34:00.110
You completely abandoned your comrades!

34:01.000 --> 34:01.880
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

34:01.880 --> 34:04.110
S-Something suddenly cropped up.

34:04.110 --> 34:05.710
The head of my department...

34:06.400 --> 34:07.200
died.

34:08.400 --> 34:10.420
So I went to deal with the aftermath.

34:10.710 --> 34:11.239
Alright,

34:11.670 --> 34:12.690
don't let it happen again.

34:12.690 --> 34:14.110
There won't be a next time.

34:14.110 --> 34:14.960
The guy is dead anyway.

34:14.960 --> 34:15.620
Qiang,

34:15.840 --> 34:16.800
you were unlucky

34:17.320 --> 34:19.670
to miss out on witnessing
the power of our team battle.

34:19.670 --> 34:20.820
That night,

34:21.230 --> 34:23.389
I just did that girl.

34:25.320 --> 34:25.909
Awesome.

34:26.000 --> 34:26.659
So awesome.

34:27.280 --> 34:29.000
Come, take a seat, everyone.

34:28.090 --> 34:29.030
[Love Guide]

34:31.400 --> 34:32.630
My dear students,

34:32.949 --> 34:36.750
[Love Guide]

34:33.070 --> 34:34.000
Xuan's success

34:34.000 --> 34:36.860
has fully demonstrated
the efficacy of our course.

34:37.190 --> 34:38.630
Xuan, I want to know,

34:38.880 --> 34:40.150
after sleeping with her,

34:40.150 --> 34:42.750
what is this chick's attitude
towards you now?

34:43.760 --> 34:46.510
She said things were
moving a bit too fast,

34:46.510 --> 34:47.190
and she needs to think about...

34:47.190 --> 34:50.389
Doesn't that mean
she doesn't want to talk to you anymore?

34:51.590 --> 34:52.590
A one-night stand

34:52.739 --> 34:55.719
[Secrets to Finding a Partner]

34:52.920 --> 34:53.920
isn't difficult.

34:54.800 --> 34:55.800
But is that interesting?

34:55.800 --> 34:56.710
No!

34:56.710 --> 34:57.320
Not at all.

34:57.510 --> 34:58.400
What's interesting is

34:57.580 --> 34:59.690
[Secrets to Finding a Partner]

34:58.590 --> 35:00.720
making a chick totally devoted to you,

35:00.800 --> 35:01.960
giving you everything she has,

35:01.960 --> 35:02.440
and even

35:02.820 --> 35:05.070
[Secrets to Finding a Partner]

35:02.880 --> 35:04.140
willing to die for you.

35:07.510 --> 35:09.630
[Five-Step Trap (Pit #5):
Emotional Abuse and Manipulation]

35:07.670 --> 35:08.470
As you can see,

35:08.880 --> 35:09.740
the fifth pit

35:10.030 --> 35:12.590
is the pinnacle of PUA Theory.

35:12.740 --> 35:15.440
[Five-Step Trap (Pit #5):
Emotional Abuse and Manipulation]

35:12.800 --> 35:13.880
Only those who are ruthless

35:13.880 --> 35:15.920
and determined to be a master manipulator

35:15.920 --> 35:18.070
are qualified to continue learning.

35:18.110 --> 35:19.400
Once you master the techniques,

35:19.400 --> 35:21.320
you can be reborn

35:21.320 --> 35:22.550
and be like me,

35:22.670 --> 35:24.070
sleeping with women
until your legs give out

35:24.070 --> 35:26.400
and counting money until your hands ache.

35:26.510 --> 35:27.670
If you want to be reborn,

35:27.670 --> 35:29.070
besides the tuition fee,

35:29.070 --> 35:31.510
you must also complete our assigned tasks.

35:32.280 --> 35:34.330
Are you confident?

35:34.480 --> 35:36.000
Yes!

35:41.110 --> 35:42.370
I screened them again.

35:42.670 --> 35:43.480
These cases

35:44.070 --> 35:45.040
aren't in our province.

35:45.040 --> 35:46.510
But judging by the elements,

35:46.510 --> 35:49.040
I think we should
investigate them together.

35:49.190 --> 35:49.850
I agree.

35:50.110 --> 35:50.800
Paw Patrol!

35:51.840 --> 35:52.500
Paw Patrol.

35:53.590 --> 35:54.190
You're eating, huh,

35:54.190 --> 35:54.670
Nan?

35:55.280 --> 35:56.680
Let me ask you a question.

36:00.760 --> 36:01.360
With lions

36:02.440 --> 36:03.110
and tigers,

36:04.150 --> 36:06.350
under what circumstances do they meet?

36:06.710 --> 36:07.640
Just spit it out.

36:13.110 --> 36:14.370
In northwestern India

36:15.550 --> 36:16.880
lives the world's

36:16.880 --> 36:17.920
only group of

36:17.780 --> 36:18.180
[Lion]

36:18.070 --> 36:20.150
wild Asiatic lions,

36:21.590 --> 36:22.840
while wild tigers

36:23.320 --> 36:25.890
are mainly distributed
far away from lions,

36:24.900 --> 36:25.580
[Lion]

36:26.070 --> 36:26.870
in South Asia,

36:27.360 --> 36:28.000
Southeast Asia,

36:28.000 --> 36:28.630
and

36:28.790 --> 36:29.760
[Lion]

36:29.070 --> 36:30.070
Russian Far East.

36:31.030 --> 36:32.190
In 2017,

36:31.490 --> 36:36.700
[Lion]

36:32.880 --> 36:34.210
in a wildlife sanctuary

36:34.320 --> 36:35.780
in Madhya Pradesh, India,

36:36.150 --> 36:39.070
an adult male Bengal tiger was found

36:36.820 --> 36:39.150
[Tiger]

36:39.260 --> 36:40.670
migrating west.

36:41.440 --> 36:42.840
It walked for two years,

36:42.900 --> 36:45.880
[Tiger]

36:43.760 --> 36:45.360
covering 300 kilometers!

36:45.880 --> 36:49.160
[300 km]

36:46.190 --> 36:47.030
It arrived

36:47.670 --> 36:48.880
at a place

36:49.220 --> 36:52.320
[480 km]

36:49.320 --> 36:52.190
only 480 kilometers away from these lions.

36:53.920 --> 36:54.440
Why?

36:55.280 --> 36:57.110
Did it have nothing better to do

36:57.110 --> 36:58.070
and just wanted to play with the lions?

36:58.070 --> 36:59.870
Say something I can understand.

37:02.440 --> 37:03.150
Food.

37:04.630 --> 37:05.890
It was because of food.

37:07.000 --> 37:08.060
That day you told me

37:08.550 --> 37:10.000
I was the only one here

37:10.000 --> 37:11.440
who had direct contact with Xia Yi,

37:11.440 --> 37:12.760
and asked me to think carefully

37:12.760 --> 37:14.710
if there were any clues I missed.

37:14.960 --> 37:15.890
I racked my brain

37:16.230 --> 37:18.190
but still couldn't figure out
what I could've missed.

37:18.190 --> 37:19.650
Household registration,

37:19.760 --> 37:21.020
immigration records,

37:21.110 --> 37:21.550
plastic surgery;

37:21.550 --> 37:23.070
we thought of everything.

37:23.440 --> 37:25.110
What do I know

37:25.190 --> 37:26.790
that the task force doesn't?

37:27.710 --> 37:29.170
And then it occurred to me.

37:34.070 --> 37:34.600
The bank.

37:37.030 --> 37:37.840
Interesting.

37:38.630 --> 37:39.190
Go on.

37:39.710 --> 37:40.320
Although

37:40.630 --> 37:41.280
Xia Yi

37:41.280 --> 37:43.810
and Lu Ban had no overlap
in border crossings,

37:44.150 --> 37:46.280
they had a common performance metric,

37:46.920 --> 37:48.320
that is hunting for prey.

37:49.590 --> 37:51.760
Just like lions and tigers.

37:52.280 --> 37:53.280
Jian Leilei and Xia Yi

37:53.280 --> 37:54.190
met at the wine auction

37:54.190 --> 37:55.440
hosted by their bank.

37:55.630 --> 37:58.070
Such an event is full of rich folk.

37:58.400 --> 37:59.570
To them,

37:59.710 --> 38:02.110
it's basically the perfect hunting ground.

38:02.110 --> 38:03.110
But I checked.

38:03.440 --> 38:04.920
Xia Yi's name wasn't on the guest list

38:04.920 --> 38:06.920
for the wine auction that day.

38:07.190 --> 38:08.840
But someone else
could have brought him in.

38:08.840 --> 38:10.840
Could the lion
who brought a tiger like Xia Yi

38:10.840 --> 38:13.110
into this perfect hunting ground

38:13.440 --> 38:14.880
be...

38:15.230 --> 38:16.130
Lu Ban?

38:22.760 --> 38:24.420
These are photos of the event.

38:25.190 --> 38:26.920
Taken by the billionaire Zhou.

38:27.710 --> 38:29.030
I went to him again

38:30.000 --> 38:32.330
and asked for all the photos
from that day.

38:32.710 --> 38:34.360
Thanks to this entrepreneur Zhou,

38:34.360 --> 38:35.670
who has a great habit

38:35.670 --> 38:37.190
of being very high-profile.

38:37.190 --> 38:38.190
No matter where he goes,

38:38.190 --> 38:40.920
he brings a professional photographer
with him.

38:42.320 --> 38:45.230
Are you saying Xia Yi isn't in the photos,

38:45.510 --> 38:46.630
but Lu Ban might be?

38:48.440 --> 38:49.770
Interrogate Cai Zhiyu.

38:50.400 --> 38:50.800
Yes.

38:53.630 --> 38:54.490
Have you eaten?

38:56.110 --> 38:56.770
So you have.

38:59.670 --> 39:00.510
Alright, then I-I'll...

39:00.510 --> 39:01.760
I'll go help Liu.

39:08.800 --> 39:09.330
My phone.

39:25.190 --> 39:25.880
Coming!

39:28.400 --> 39:28.960
Who is it?

39:31.960 --> 39:32.420
Come in.

39:34.030 --> 39:35.030
Is it a bad time?

39:35.030 --> 39:35.800
No, no, it's fine.

39:35.800 --> 39:37.320
I-I was just working out.

39:37.320 --> 39:38.190
Come on in.

39:43.000 --> 39:43.800
Sit, sit.

39:48.030 --> 39:48.830
What's wrong?

39:50.550 --> 39:51.880
I just wanted to tell you

39:51.960 --> 39:53.300
that Yu Kexin and Xia Yi

39:53.400 --> 39:55.800
were indeed both in that PUA organization.

39:57.710 --> 40:00.170
Does that mean
we can find Xia Yi through her?

40:00.190 --> 40:01.150
Yu Kexin said

40:01.510 --> 40:03.760
Xia Yi used to be her mentor

40:04.190 --> 40:05.800
and the first person to gaslight her.

40:05.800 --> 40:06.190
Wait.

40:07.550 --> 40:08.590
So she's a victim

40:08.590 --> 40:09.630
just like Leilei?

40:10.480 --> 40:10.920
Yes.

40:12.360 --> 40:14.280
But after Yu Kexin recovered,

40:14.480 --> 40:16.210
she decided to become a hunter.

40:16.440 --> 40:19.190
She said she and Xia Yi are now wingmen,

40:19.550 --> 40:22.610
often leaving messages in a game
to contact each other.

40:23.510 --> 40:24.410
She also said

40:24.880 --> 40:26.740
the organization is very strict.

40:26.920 --> 40:28.690
You only get to see

40:28.880 --> 40:30.400
the most core evidence

40:30.510 --> 40:31.880
during the forbidden technique stage.

40:31.880 --> 40:34.110
And the task to enter
the forbidden technique stage

40:34.110 --> 40:35.850
is exactly as Zhang Yaozu said:

40:36.070 --> 40:37.130
shoot a video of you

40:37.230 --> 40:37.920
getting intimate,

40:37.920 --> 40:39.710
with faces and the tattoo showing.

40:39.710 --> 40:40.520
So this task

40:40.840 --> 40:42.610
is like a pledge of loyalty

40:42.710 --> 40:44.510
to ensure you won't report them.

40:45.320 --> 40:47.230
Yes, I-I know that.

40:51.920 --> 40:52.630
Lu.

40:55.400 --> 40:57.210
If you are going to shoot that video,

40:57.210 --> 40:57.680
I...

41:01.320 --> 41:01.880
No, no!

41:01.880 --> 41:03.110
Sorry, I didn't know Fang Fang was here.

41:03.110 --> 41:04.590
No, no! It's not Fang Fang.

41:05.800 --> 41:06.840
Not Fang Fang?

41:06.920 --> 41:07.630
No, no.

41:07.880 --> 41:08.400
Well,

41:08.480 --> 41:09.110
s-she is...

41:09.110 --> 41:10.400
You sure are quick to pick up bad habits!

41:10.400 --> 41:11.200
That's not it!

41:11.630 --> 41:12.230
Come... Come here.

41:12.230 --> 41:12.800
Take a look.

41:12.800 --> 41:14.190
Look at what? I'm leaving.

41:14.190 --> 41:15.000
Don't leave!

41:15.000 --> 41:15.320
Wait.

41:15.320 --> 41:16.840
Take a look
and you'll know what's going on.

41:16.840 --> 41:18.000
You want me to look at that?

41:18.000 --> 41:18.510
You're mistaken!

41:18.510 --> 41:19.070
Let me go!

41:19.190 --> 41:20.230
I'm not that dirty.

41:20.230 --> 41:21.840
Come here. Just take a look.

41:21.840 --> 41:23.190
Come on, I beg you.

41:23.190 --> 41:24.400
Come on, take a look.

41:24.400 --> 41:25.710
Just take a look.

41:25.710 --> 41:26.150
No, really.

41:26.150 --> 41:27.510
You'll understand once you look at it.

41:27.510 --> 41:28.710
Look. Look.

41:34.280 --> 41:35.380
It's all fake.

41:35.710 --> 41:36.230
Look.

41:36.230 --> 41:36.960
Look at this.

41:37.000 --> 41:37.320
It's

41:37.840 --> 41:38.590
s-so fake.

41:40.760 --> 41:42.670
You want to fool them with this?

41:44.070 --> 41:45.400
How is that possible?

41:46.590 --> 41:47.960
If this could work,

41:48.320 --> 41:50.380
would Zhang Yaozu have looked for me?

41:50.630 --> 41:53.150
This is the only way
I-I could've thought of.

41:57.840 --> 41:58.800
I have an idea.

41:59.830 --> 42:04.410
[The Dark Romance]

42:10.760 --> 42:11.440
Hey, you...

42:12.150 --> 42:13.670
Don't, don't.

42:14.110 --> 42:15.070
P-Put your clothes on.

42:15.070 --> 42:15.590
Lu.

42:15.760 --> 42:16.280
Look at me.

42:16.280 --> 42:17.070
I can't!

42:17.070 --> 42:18.070
It's only married people...

42:18.070 --> 42:18.920
Look at me!

42:25.840 --> 42:26.640
It's painted?

42:33.400 --> 42:34.280
Are you crazy?

42:36.280 --> 42:38.610
This is the only way
I could've thought of.

42:39.960 --> 42:41.960
I want to help you complete the video

42:42.320 --> 42:43.720
to get the core evidence.

42:45.480 --> 42:46.590
I promised Leilei

42:47.230 --> 42:48.520
to clear her name.

42:48.630 --> 42:49.870
You... You...

42:50.320 --> 42:50.960
No, you...

42:50.960 --> 42:51.850
I-I...

42:52.920 --> 42:53.650
Goodness...

42:54.570 --> 42:55.340
Well,

42:55.400 --> 42:57.670
we will just be posing, right?

42:59.710 --> 43:00.170
Well,

43:00.800 --> 43:01.630
what else?

43:02.710 --> 43:05.320
I... I-I thought it was just posing too.
